<topic xmlns:ditaarch="http://dita.oasis-open.org/architecture/2005/" id="ug-pi-d">
  <title>Insert/Edit PI Dialog</title>
  <body id="body">
    <section>
      <p>The <term>Insert/Edit PI Dialog</term> allows you to create or modify processing instructions (PIs). New PIs will be inserted at the current cursor position.</p>
      <fig>
        <title>Insert/Edit PI Dialog</title>
        <image href="editPiDialog.gif" align="center" placement="break"/>
      </fig>
      <p>For example, the dialog above will create the following PI:</p>
      <screen>&lt;?mypi test?&gt;</screen>
    </section>
  </body>
</topic>
